=== 巴林湖人 ===

人类学家{{le|约瑟夫·伯塞尔|Joseph Birdsell}}将[[澳大利亚原住民|澳大利亚原住民]]分为三类：卡奔塔利亚湾人（{{lang|en|Carpentarians}}）、墨累河人（{{lang|en|Murrayians}}）、巴林湖人（{{lang-en|Barrineans}}）。其中巴林湖人得名于{{Link-en|巴林湖|Lake Barrine}}（{{lang-en|Lake Barrine}}），他们身高比其他原住民矮。除了巴林湖一带的原住民，[[塔斯马尼亚原住民|塔斯马尼亚原住民]]也被伯塞尔归为巴林湖人。伯塞尔认为巴林湖人是最早定居于澳大利亚的矮黑人遗存，然而遗传学研究表明他们和其他澳大利亚原住民同源，且与东南亚矮黑人关系较远。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Australian Barrineans and Their Relationship to Southeast Asian Negritos: An Investigation using Mitochondrial Genomics|url=https://bioone.org/journals/human-biology/volume-85/issue-1_2f_3/027.085.0322/The-Australian-Barrineans-and-Their-Relationship-to-Southeast-Asian-Negritos/10.3378/027.085.0322.full|last=Mcallister|first=Peter|last2=Nagle|first2=Nano|date=2013/06|journal=Human Biology|issue=1/3|doi=10.3378/027.085.0322|volume=85|pages=485–502|issn=0018-7143|last3=Mitchell|first3=Robert John}}</ref>他们的身高虽然偏矮，但明显比非洲俾格米人和亚洲尼格利陀人高，因此不算作俾格米人。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The extinction of rigour: a comment on 'The extinction of the Australian Pygmies' by Keith Windschuttle and Tim Gillin|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/24046693|last=Westaway|first=Michael|last2=Hiscock|first2=Peter|date=2005|journal=Aboriginal History|volume=29|pages=142–148|issn=0314-8769|access-date=2021-02-14|archive-date=2020-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200311183824/https://www.jstor.org/stable/24046693}}</ref>

